metadata.name: Weightlessness
metadata.description: We all live in the whirlwind of life, we are covered by the waves of life's storms, then we find ourselves in the calm, begging fate for at least a little breeze that would fill our sails of life. But how useful it is sometimes to just stop, relax and hear yourself, feel the weightlessness of your body, clear your thoughts of unnecessary worries and experiences, and reset yourself.
